Package org.testsuite.data

In this package the data classes are summarized.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TestEventListener
    Defines all events for the tests.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Config
    Saves the configuration from the configuration file.
    Data
    In this class attributes are implemented, which are used both in the test class and in the test suite class.
    Fit
    Saves the data for a Fit Test
    Junit
    Saves the data for a junit test
    Library
    Stores the information in a library.
    Test
    In this class, the data are stored into a text.
    TestEvent
    Stores all necessary data for a test event.
    TestSelectEvent
    Stores all necessary data for a test select event.
    TestSuite
    Saves the data for a test suite.
